# Region Changelog Template

When updating `CHANGELOG.md` for region data changes, use this app-friendly format:

```markdown
## YYYY-MM-DD

### 简化事件（用于 App 展示）
- [地域上线] <云厂商> | <地域> | <region_code> | <上线日期 YYYY-MM-DD>
- [地域变更] <云厂商> | <地域> | <说明>
- [地域新增可用区] <云厂商> | <地域> | <新增 AZ 列表>
```

Guidelines:
- Keep one entry per change batch/date.
- Simplified event types: `地域上线`, `地域变更`, `地域新增可用区`. **AZ changes (add/remove/correct mappings) are 地域变更, not 地域下线.** Do **not** use `[地域下线]`.
- `地域新增可用区` is only for newly listed AZs; use `地域变更` for AZ removals, corrections, channel/site wording, coordinates, etc.
- Use a **数据修正** subsection for lengthy technical notes alongside simplified lines when helpful.
- Keep each event line in one unified format: `[类型] 厂商 | 地域 | 详情` (fourth field launch date required only for `地域上线`).
